## ══════════════════════════════════════════════
## PART 4 — PCL → GLC PATTERN MAP
## (What every section looks like and which CSS pattern to use)
## ══════════════════════════════════════════════

This is the master translation of PCL Construction's layout DNA into GLC's design language.
Every section on every page maps to one of these patterns.

```
PCL PATTERN                                  GLC IMPLEMENTATION                          CSS PATTERN
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Preloader intro animation              →  Charcoal → logo reveal + progress bar       #gl-preloader
Full-bleed hero slider (3-5 images)    →  3-slide crossfade hero + service bar        .hero__slide / .hero__service-bar
Mega-menu sticky nav                   →  Mega nav (Services + Company dropdowns)     .gl-mega--services / .gl-mega--company
Rotating declaratives strip            →  Yellow marquee trust ticker                 .gl-marquee
Editorial white-space split sections   →  About split (charcoal ground, 1fr/1fr)      #about / .about__inner
Project photo tile grid w/ overlays    →  6 Services photo tile grid                  .services__grid / .svc-tile
Animated stats dashboard               →  4-stat counter row (white bg)               #stats / .stat-cell[data-counter]
Featured project case-study showcase   →  2-3 featured project panels (wide + 2)      .projects__grid / .project-panel
Zigzag split why-us section            →  "Why Ground Level" 4-reason split           #why / .why__reasons
Office/coverage map section            →  Coverage region list + map                  #coverage / .coverage__areas
News + Insights editorial grid         →  Testimonials 3-card grid                    #testimonials / .testimonial-card
Dual CTA ("Project / Career")          →  Dual CTA ("Project / Contact")              #cta / .cta__panels
4-col dark footer w/ sustainability    →  4-col dark footer                           #footer / .footer__main
```

### Section Background Alternation Rule
Every page must alternate section backgrounds in this order (never two adjacent sections the same):

```
--charcoal-deep  (Hero / Preloader)
--yellow-core    (Marquee strip — always immediately after hero)
--charcoal       (About / Why / Coverage)
--white          (Stats / Projects)
--off-white      (Services / Process / Testimonials)
--charcoal-deep  (CTA / Footer)
```

### 3-Plane Depth Rule (ALL sections must follow)
Every section has three to 4 four visual layers:
1. **GROUND** — The section background (flat color, never gradient except radial accents)
2. **STRUCTURE** — Architectural elements: rails, clip-paths, photo shells, grid tiles
3. **READ** — The typography and CTAs on the top surface

Never place body text (`--text-500`) directly on a dark background. Use `--font-body` white variants (`.gl-prose--light` / `color:rgba(255,255,255,0.62)`) on dark sections.

