## ══════════════════════════════════════════════
## PART 5 — FULL COMPONENT LIBRARY
## ══════════════════════════════════════════════

All components defined here are already in `GLC_MASTER_SYSTEM.html`. Use these classes — never create one-off styles.

### Typography Classes
| Class | Use |
|---|---|
| `.gl-h1` | Oswald 700 uppercase, clamp(52px→88px), H1 only |
| `.gl-h2` | Oswald 700 uppercase, clamp(36px→54px), section headlines |
| `.gl-h3` | Oswald 700 uppercase, clamp(20px→28px), card/tile titles |
| `.gl-eyebrow` | 11px/800/uppercase yellow, always above a headline, has `::before` yellow line |
| `.gl-eyebrow--dark` | Eyebrow on light backgrounds |
| `.gl-eyebrow--light` | Eyebrow on dark backgrounds (white text, yellow line) |
| `.gl-prose` | 15px body, `--text-500` — light section use only |
| `.gl-prose--light` | White/62% opacity — dark section body text |
| `.gl-prose--sm` | 13px body variant |
| `.gl-pullquote` | Source Serif 4 italic — flagship pull-quotes only |
| `.gl-metric--lg` | Oswald 700, clamp(48px→72px), stat numbers |
| `.gl-metric--md` | Oswald 700, clamp(32px→48px) |
| `.gl-metric--accent` | Yellow stat numbers |

### Button System
| Class | Use |
|---|---|
| `.gl-btn` | Base button class — ALWAYS include with a modifier |
| `.gl-btn--primary` | Yellow fill, dark text — primary CTA |
| `.gl-btn--ghost` | Transparent, white border — on dark sections |
| `.gl-btn--ghost-dark` | Transparent, dark border — on light sections |
| `.gl-btn--link` | Text-only arrow link, yellow |
| `.gl-btn__arrow` | Arrow SVG inside button — gets `translateX` on hover |

### Scroll Reveal
| Class | Use |
|---|---|
| `.gl-reveal` | Default: fade up 24px |
| `.gl-reveal--up` | Stronger fade up 40px |
| `.gl-reveal--left` | Fade in from left |
| `.gl-reveal--right` | Fade in from right |
| `.gl-reveal--scale` | Scale up from 0.94 |
| `.gl-delay-1` through `.gl-delay-5` | Stagger delays (0.1s → 0.5s) |

Add `.gl-reveal` to every visible content block. JS (`IntersectionObserver`) handles the rest — no changes needed.

### Layout Patterns (Catalog Reference)

#### A-Series — Grid Layouts
| ID | Pattern | Use |
|---|---|---|
| A1 | Full-bleed photo panel | Hero, project panels, wide showcase panels |
| A3 | Staggered tile grid | Services grid (3-col), testimonials (3-col) |
| A4 | Off-grid floating accent | Float stat chips, About media float badges |
| A5 | Horizontal scroll rail | Mobile service bar |
| A6 | Partial border frame | Why section photo border treatment |

#### B-Series — Split / Stack Layouts
| ID | Pattern | Use |
|---|---|---|
| B2 | Full-bleed media split | About (1fr/1fr, charcoal bg), Why (mirrored) |
| B4 | Statement band / pull-quote | Dual CTA panels |
| B6 | Sticky scope strip | Inner service pages — sub-nav anchors |
| B7 | Accordion | Service detail FAQ sections |
| B8 | Vertical stepper | Process section (4-step rail) |
| B9 | Hub stage card | Service detail flagship section (split panel + spec deck) |

#### C-Series — Data / Dashboard
| ID | Pattern | Use |
|---|---|---|
| C2 | Tri-column specs/stats | Stats row (4 cells with counters) |
| C3 | Masonry grid | Projects page filter grid |

### Component: Service Tile (`.svc-tile`)
```html
<a href="/services/[slug]/" class="svc-tile gl-reveal">
  <div class="svc-tile__bg" style="background-image:url('...')"></div>
  <div class="svc-tile__overlay"></div>
  <div class="svc-tile__content">
    <div class="svc-tile__num">01</div>
    <div class="svc-tile__title">Service Name</div>
    <div class="svc-tile__desc">Short description.</div>
    <div class="svc-tile__arrow">View Service →</div>
  </div>
</a>
```
- Yellow top bar scales in on hover (`::before` scaleX)
- Description and arrow reveal on hover (max-height / opacity transition)

### Component: Project Panel (`.project-panel`)
```html
<a href="/projects/[slug]/" class="project-panel [project-panel--wide] gl-reveal">
  <div class="project-panel__bg" style="background-image:url('...')"></div>
  <div class="project-panel__scrim"></div>
  <div class="project-panel__info">
    <span class="project-panel__tag">Category</span>
    <div class="project-panel__title">Project Name</div>
    <div class="project-panel__meta">Location • Year</div>
    <div class="project-panel__cta">View Project →</div>
  </div>
</a>
```
- Add `.project-panel--wide` to first panel (spans 2 cols, 21:9 ratio)

### Component: Stat Cell (`.stat-cell`)
```html
<div class="stat-cell gl-reveal" data-counter="500">
  <span class="stat-cell__num"><span class="counter-val">500</span><span class="stat-cell__suffix">+</span></span>
  <span class="stat-cell__label">Label</span>
  <span class="stat-cell__sub">Subtext</span>
</div>
```
- `data-counter` value is the target number. JS animates from 0 on scroll.
- Yellow bottom bar slides in on hover

### Component: Testimonial Card (`.testimonial-card`)
```html
<div class="testimonial-card gl-reveal">
  <span class="testimonial-card__mark">"</span>
  <p class="testimonial-card__text">Quote text...</p>
  <div class="testimonial-card__rule"></div>
  <div class="testimonial-card__name">First Last</div>
  <div class="testimonial-card__role">Title, Company</div>
</div>
```

### Component: Why Reason (`.why__reason`)
