### `/index.html` — Homepage Migration
**Section sequence (in order):**

1. `#gl-preloader` — Charcoal fullscreen logo reveal
2. `<header id="gl-header">` — Mega nav (verbatim copy)
3. `#hero` — Full-bleed 3-slide crossfade hero + service bar
   - Slides: excavation site / foundations pour / grading operation
   - Overlay stat cards (right column): years + projects + regions
   - Service bar: 6 icons below hero fold
4. `.gl-marquee` — Yellow trust ticker (immediately after hero, no gap)
5. `#about` — Charcoal 50/50 split: photo (clip-path) left / copy right
6. `#stats` — White 4-stat counter row (animated on scroll)
7. `#services` — Off-white 6-tile photo grid (3×2)
8. `#projects` — White featured project panels (1 wide + 2 standard)
9. `#why` — Charcoal-deep 50/50 split: copy+reasons left / photo right
10. `#process` — Off-white 4-step horizontal stepper
11. `#coverage` — Charcoal coverage region cards + map
12. `#testimonials` — Off-white 3-card testimonial grid
13. `#cta` — Dual CTA panels: yellow (Start a Project) + dark (Contact)
14. `<footer id="footer">` — 4-col dark footer (verbatim copy)

