## ══════════════════════════════════════════════
## PART 7 — MASTER JAVASCRIPT BLOCK
## ══════════════════════════════════════════════

Paste this entire `<script>` block at the bottom of `<body>` on **every page**.
Copy verbatim from `GLC_MASTER_SYSTEM.html` — do not split into separate files unless extracting to `site.js`.

The script handles:
- `#gl-preloader` fade-out on `window.load`
- `.scrolled` class on `#gl-header` after 40px scroll
- Mega menu hover + backdrop + keyboard (Enter/Space/Escape)
- Mobile drawer open/close/overlay
- Hero crossfade slider with dot navigation (5500ms interval)
- `.gl-reveal` scroll reveal via IntersectionObserver
- `[data-counter]` animated number counters (1800ms ease-out cubic)
- `.gl-accordion__trigger` accordion toggle
- `.gl-scope-strip__link` scroll spy (rootMargin `-40% 0px -55% 0px`)
- Smooth anchor scroll with `--header-total-h` offset

---

## ══════════════════════════════════════════════
## PART 8 — HARD RULES (ABSOLUTE — NEVER VIOLATE)
## ══════════════════════════════════════════════

```
[RULE 01]  Brand yellow is ONLY #F2B705 — accessed via var(--yellow-core). Never approximate with #FFB800, #F5BC00, or any other value.
[RULE 02]  border-radius is ZERO everywhere. Only border-radius:50% on decorative circles (e.g., coverage dot, marquee separator). No rounded cards, no rounded buttons, no rounded inputs.
[RULE 03]  Font stack: Oswald for all display/headings, Plus Jakarta Sans for all body/UI, Source Serif 4 italic for pull-quotes ONLY. No other fonts.
[RULE 04]  --container-max:1200px is the hard maximum. No section content exceeds this width.
[RULE 05]  Never place --text-500 grey body text directly on a dark section background. Use gl-prose--light (white/62%) instead.
[RULE 06]  Never create one-off button styles. Use only the .gl-btn class system.
[RULE 07]  Never create one-off type styles. Use only the .gl-h1/.gl-h2/.gl-h3/.gl-eyebrow/.gl-prose class system.
[RULE 08]  All transitions use var(--ease-expo) — cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1). Never use linear or ease-in-out for UI transitions.
[RULE 09]  --gap-grid:2px between tiles and panels is intentional. Do not increase this gap.
[RULE 10]  The nav and footer HTML structure is fixed. Never alter the .gl-header__ or .footer__ class trees. Only add modifier classes.
[RULE 11]  Never use gradient backgrounds for section fills — only flat CSS color tokens. Gradients are allowed only for photo scrims and subtle radial texture overlays.
[RULE 12]  Section padding uses --section-v (96px) for standard and --section-v-sm (64px) for compact. Never use arbitrary pixel values for section vertical padding.
[RULE 13]  All visible content blocks must have .gl-reveal. Use .gl-delay-1 through .gl-delay-5 to stagger items in a sequence.
[RULE 14]  Service tile images use aspect-ratio:4/3. Project panels use 16:10 (standard) or 21:9 (wide/hero). Never alter these ratios.
[RULE 15]  Yellow (#F2B705) is a structural color used for: accent bars, eyebrow lines, stat numbers, hover borders, CTA primary background. It is NEVER used as a large section background except the marquee strip and the primary CTA panel.
```

---

## ══════════════════════════════════════════════
## PART 9 — RESPONSIVE BREAKPOINTS
## ══════════════════════════════════════════════

```css
/* Tablet — @media (max-width: 1024px) */
.hero__content-inner     → single column (stats panel hidden)
.hero__service-bar-grid  → 3 columns
.about__inner, .why__inner → single column (media stacks above copy)
.services__header        → single column
.services__grid          → 2 columns
.stats__inner            → 2×2 grid
.testimonials__grid      → 2 columns
.projects__grid          → single column (wide panel loses --wide)
.coverage__inner         → single column
.coverage__areas         → 2 columns
.footer__main            → 2 columns (brand spans full width)

/* Mobile — @media (max-width: 768px) */
:root → --section-v becomes 64px
.gl-header__utility, .gl-header__nav → hidden
.gl-header__mobile → flex (hamburger + mobile logo)
.hero__service-bar-grid → 2 columns
.services__grid, .testimonials__grid → single column
.stats__inner → 2×2
.process__steps → 2×2 (rail hidden)
.coverage__areas → single column
.cta__panels → single column
.footer__main → single column, 20px padding
.footer__bar-inner → flex-direction:column
```

